    "The dataset from these two courses includes 1044 students, and the mathematics course contains 395 records, while the dataset for the Portuguese language course contains 649 records.",
    "These two-courses datasets include data on student's grades and demographic, social, and academic features that were gathered by using school reports and questionnaires.",
    "The UCI machine learning repository has been used by Aslam et al (2021); Begum and Padmannavar (2022); Liu et al (2022b); Yang et al (2022); Yousafzai et al (2021) for developing student's academic performance predictive models.",
    "• Learner Activity Tracker Tool called Alibaba Cloud Tianchi's xAPI-Edu-Data, which is an extensive collection of educational data from more than 10 million students who use the online learning platform.",
    "The xAPI dataset includes 480 student records and 16 features of student's demographics, their educational activities, and their performance in various courses."
